Package: survtabler
Title: Wrappers for Fast, Concise, and Easy-to-Read Survival Analysis
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Jaakko", "Koskenniemi", , "jajoko@utu.fi", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-9348-3325"))
Description: 
    Survtabler helps to make survival analysis scripts function-based. This 
    reduces unnecessary repetition and is therefore quick to write and easy to read.
